    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个叫伊卡的男孩要去看海。出身在一个穷兵黩武的帝国，他对战争和发明兵器感到厌倦。用偷来的【飞翼】改造了一艘老炮艇后，伊卡开始了逃亡之旅。据说，“船”本是用来“航行”的，但在这个世界里，海已经消失大半个世纪了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乘坐炮艇逃离战场，横跨伊卡利亚大陆，欣赏禁区外的广阔世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145750/extras/359076f08261e63af72ca12f23bc6440.poster.avif?t=1741798358\" width=720 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145750/extras/359076f08261e63af72ca12f23bc6440.webm?t=1741798358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145750/extras/359076f08261e63af72ca12f23bc6440.mp4?t=1741798358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调度大炮、发射导弹，维修引擎...但请注意，操控老旧的炮艇系统需要<strong>手动键入指令</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145750/extras/3eff451221c4605d72b97d73ac15cd91.poster.avif?t=1741798358\" width=800 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145750/extras/3eff451221c4605d72b97d73ac15cd91.webm?t=1741798358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145750/extras/3eff451221c4605d72b97d73ac15cd91.mp4?t=1741798358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎击各式各样的敌人——凭借你的观察和<strong>打字手速</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145750/extras/670cce423eb0ad66182c48fad76af998.poster.avif?t=1741798358\" width=720 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145750/extras/670cce423eb0ad66182c48fad76af998.webm?t=1741798358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145750/extras/670cce423eb0ad66182c48fad76af998.mp4?t=1741798358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关于</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>这个小游戏始于一次gamejam，怀着对经典弹幕射击、打字游戏和90年代动漫的热爱，我们大胆尝试了这个颇具实验性的玩法组合。在调整、润色多轮后，我们想让更多玩家体验这个创意，因此决定将它免费发布。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>游戏包含6个关卡和一段精心创作的奇幻故事，希望你能喜欢。</i></p>",
